1
00:00:07,760 --> 00:00:11,019
♪I read the seconds♪

2
00:00:11,020 --> 00:00:14,528
♪Waiting for dawn♪

3
00:00:14,528 --> 00:00:17,069
♪After the dawn♪

4
00:00:17,070 --> 00:00:20,059
♪The sun rises♪

5
00:00:20,060 --> 00:00:21,719
♪I am the flower blooming at night♪

6
00:00:21,720 --> 00:00:23,579
♪And also the eruption of a volcano♪

7
00:00:23,580 --> 00:00:26,779
♪I am the bowing wooden horse♪

8
00:00:26,780 --> 00:00:30,608
♪And also the broken sword
wandering the world♪

9
00:00:33,120 --> 00:00:33,930
=From God to Husband=

10
00:00:33,930 --> 00:00:36,224
(Adapted from "From God to Husband"
by Yueyingguxiangming)

11
00:00:36,230 --> 00:00:37,984
=Episode 1=

12
00:00:45,840 --> 00:00:47,456
(Mausoleum of Fairy)

13
00:00:51,560 --> 00:00:53,240
It has been seven hundred years.

14
00:00:53,800 --> 00:00:57,440
(Demon Lord)
I am finally out.

15
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:02,960
Demon Lord, how dare you
trespass the Demon Slayer Path!

16
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:04,960
(Zhu Que)
Do you not know who guards this place?

17
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:08,440
Today, I shall slay the Northern Lord

18
00:01:08,720 --> 00:01:10,160
and unite the Immortal Realm!

19
00:01:10,160 --> 00:01:11,750
(Tomb of My Wife Liu Chenfei)
Jiang Northern Lord!

20
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:13,120
Prepare to die!

21
00:01:18,144 --> 00:01:21,200
(Jiang Feng, Northern Lord)

22
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:26,920
Disturbing my peace,

23
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:28,720
you shall be slain!

24
00:01:41,100 --> 00:01:42,544
(Qing Long)
It's the Tiangang Sword!

25
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,720
With just this one sword,

26
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:46,120
he deserves the title of Northern Lord.

27
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,080
Since you have come,

28
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:52,000
just stay here.

29
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:56,720
Petty tricks.

30
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,000
Jiang Northern Lord,

31
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:01,200
I'll kill you!

32
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:02,800
Interesting.

33
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:31,710
(Bai Hu)
The second sword!

34
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:33,180
(Bai Hu)
Such terrifying spiritual pressure!

35
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:35,280
We can hardly
keep our eyes open from a distance.

36
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,680
It's the third sword
of the Northern Lord!

37
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:54,000
(Xuan Wu)
I have lived for over a thousand years,

38
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:58,880
yet it is fortunate to witness
the third sword of the Northern Lord.

39
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:03,720
Impossible!

40
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,480
Such a level of sword energy...

41
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,560
You...

42
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:09,280
You've already broken through
to the Divine Realm,

43
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:11,040
and become the Immortal Emperor!

44
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:12,000
No!

45
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,440
Spare my life!

46
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:14,960
I am willing to join your ranks.

47
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:17,280
If everyone could live by surrendering,

48
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,320
then what would be

49
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,120
the point of rules?

50
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:23,680
Sever!

51
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:37,400
Congratulations on breaking
through the Divine Realm,

52
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:39,440
and ascending
to the Nine Extremes Immortal Emperor!

53
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:42,000
I have more
important things to attend to.

54
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:44,112
I have cultivated for a thousand years,

55
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:46,160
for this very day.

56
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:48,400
Chenfei,

57
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:50,880
wait for me.

58
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:57,680
A rift in time and space!

59
00:03:58,320 --> 00:04:00,560
Are you intending to reverse time?

60
00:04:00,570 --> 00:04:02,600
Such an action would greatly
damage your cultivation.

61
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:04,000
Please reconsider, Northern Lord!

62
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,280
No need to persuade me.

63
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:07,720
Back then, I was framed by a villain,

64
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,430
and accidentally
entered the Immortal Realm,

65
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:11,880
which led Chenfei
to a dead end and desperate suicide.

66
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:14,480
Now that I have broken through,

67
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:16,760
it is time to reverse time,

68
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:18,200
and change everything.

69
00:04:18,880 --> 00:04:20,480
You all, fulfill your duties,

70
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,720
and protect the people.

71
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:24,320
I have someone
more important to protect.

72
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:25,320
Northern Lord,

73
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:26,400
if you do this,

74
00:04:26,464 --> 00:04:28,320
not only will you lose your cultivation,

75
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:30,090
but you'll also be left
weakened and trapped.

76
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:31,200
For Chenfei,

77
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:34,320
a mere thousand years
of cultivation is nothing.

78
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,640
I am finally back.

79
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:50,840
Chenfei,

80
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:51,760
wait for me.

81
00:04:53,088 --> 00:04:54,160
(Lu Family, top family)

82
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:55,880
(of Jiangcheng)
Grandpa! What's wrong?

83
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:57,408
(Master Lu of Lu Family)

84
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:59,080
Mountains and rivers change,

85
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:00,270
and the world change color.

86
00:05:00,280 --> 00:05:02,752
(Lu Hongling, Young Master)
A powerful being is coming here!

87
00:05:02,752 --> 00:05:03,960
(Kong Family of Jiangcheng)

88
00:05:03,960 --> 00:05:05,400
You unfilial son!

89
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:14,960
Why has an unparalleled spiritual power
suddenly descended upon Jiangcheng?

90
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:16,760
(Master Kong Tianhai)
To cause such a disturbance,

91
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:19,880
(of Kong Family)
his strength must far exceed my own.

92
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:22,128
(Year of 2024, Jiangcheng)

93
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:26,640
Everything still feels so familiar.

94
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,000
(Chenfei,)

95
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:30,960
(back when I was betrayed
by Kong Mingzhe and died,)

96
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:33,320
(I spent a thousand years
to return to the mortal realm.)

97
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:35,000
(Now, I want to change all of this.)

98
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,520
(I'll protect you and save your life.)

99
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:38,840
I went through much trouble
to have you married into the Liu family.

100
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:42,160
To prevent you from getting involved
in the Jiang family's catastrophe.

101
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,840
Feng, run away!

102
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:45,640
You must live well.

103
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:47,520
You're idle and unambitious.

104
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:48,520
I really don't understand

105
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:49,960
why Grandpa wanted me to marry you.

106
00:05:50,280 --> 00:05:51,080
Hurry up!

107
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:53,280
Are you done?

108
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:55,840
He's thoroughly dead, Young Master.

109
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:58,320
(Kong Mingzhe, Young Master)
No one will covet Miss Chenfei anymore.

110
00:05:58,440 --> 00:05:59,280
Let's go.

111
00:06:10,352 --> 00:06:12,910
(Limitless Immortal Sovereign)

112
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:24,960
I didn't expect such a talented person
in the mortal world.

113
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:26,640
Forget it.

114
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:29,880
I'll make an exception
and take you as my disciple.

115
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:31,960
Whether you can enter the Immortal Gate

116
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:34,160
depends on your own fortune,

117
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,160
Jiang Feng.

118
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,080
Tonight is the day

119
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:42,080
when Chenfei committed suicide
in her previous life.

120
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,200
Oh no!

121
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:58,760
(Too bad! There's no way out.)

122
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,160
Ms. Liu,

123
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,440
on this joyous day,

124
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:05,200
don't keep Young Master Kong
waiting anxiously.

125
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,960
When we start fighting later,

126
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,320
if my men hurt you,

127
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:10,080
it wouldn't be good.

128
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:12,760
Don't come closer.

129
00:07:14,928 --> 00:07:16,630
(Liu Chenfei)

130
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:17,840
Why is everyone

131
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:21,760
forcing me to marry
that useless son of the Kong family?

132
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:23,960
Jiang Feng.

133
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:28,400
Do you know
how I've spent these three years?

134
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,840
Subjected to humiliation,

135
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:33,520
and swallowing my anger.

136
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:36,960
If there is a next life,

137
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,960
I would rather
have no connection with you.

138
00:07:58,680 --> 00:07:59,760
Chenfei!

139
00:08:00,380 --> 00:08:03,369
♪Watching the twilight, vast and deep♪

140
00:08:03,370 --> 00:08:06,496
♪Turn into the desolation of the night♪

141
00:08:06,768 --> 00:08:08,720
♪Through many separations♪

142
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:10,429
♪How can we miss it♪

143
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:14,729
♪I am willing
to burn this life into fire♪

144
00:08:14,730 --> 00:08:16,480
♪The troubles fade away♪

145
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,480
♪No more separations♪

146
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:20,920
What's happening?

147
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:21,760
How come I...

148
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:24,400
It's you?

149
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:28,640
Chenfei.

150
00:08:32,040 --> 00:08:34,240
How dare you come back to see me?

151
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:37,040
Do you know

152
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:39,920
that Grandpa went through
so much trouble

153
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,240
to take you

154
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,480
into our Liu family?

155
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,920
Since then, our Liu Company

156
00:08:45,168 --> 00:08:46,160
has faced difficulties,

157
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:48,040
surrounded by enemies.

158
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,880
Grandpa's health deteriorated,

159
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:51,800
suffering from illness.

160
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,960
Where were you then?

161
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:55,840
Chenfei...

162
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:59,190
To save Grandpa from his severe illness,

163
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,600
I sought medical help everywhere.

164
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:04,760
To restore the Liu family,

165
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,840
I endured humiliation.

166
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,720
Where were you then?

167
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:12,200
Even now,

168
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:13,600
I am forced to remarry,

169
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,640
only to seek death

170
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,640
for a shred of dignity.

171
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:18,080
Chenfei...

172
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:18,920
And pride!

173
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,120
Jiang Feng.

174
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,480
Do you know

175
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:27,000
that every moment and every second

176
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:29,880
of these three years

177
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:32,120
has been torment?

178
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:34,000
(I feel the same as you.)

179
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:37,320
(You don't know that I've endured
torment for a whole thousand years.)

180
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,000
Chenfei.

181
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:42,240
I deeply know that I owe you too much.

182
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:44,360
But there are some misunderstandings.

183
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,240
It wasn't my intention to leave.

184
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,600
No matter what happened in the past,

185
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:50,000
now that I am back,

186
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,320
I'm here to make it up to you.

187
00:09:52,900 --> 00:09:54,370
Whatever difficulties you encounter,

188
00:09:54,384 --> 00:09:55,456
you can tell me.

189
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,360
This time,

190
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,104
I will protect you

191
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,608
and the Liu family.

192
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,960
The Liu family will be reborn.

193
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,120
It will enjoy supreme honor.

194
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:05,760
And you'll become the brightest
pearl in the entire Jiangcheng. Alright?

195
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:06,760
Don't you think

196
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:09,960
that what you're saying is ridiculous?

197
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,608
I don't believe a single word of it.

198
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:48,016
♪Immortal clouds drift
in the wave of smoke♪

199
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:51,408
♪Suddenly become a guest
in the mortal world again♪

200
00:10:51,904 --> 00:10:54,832
♪The cause and effect of deep feelings♪

201
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:57,840
♪The choices that break the heart♪

202
00:10:58,752 --> 00:11:01,184
♪But this heart has already been locked♪

203
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:04,880
♪Deep feelings have never changed♪

204
00:11:05,152 --> 00:11:08,576
♪What does it matter
if the wind and clouds rise again♪

205
00:11:08,704 --> 00:11:12,064
♪I live for you♪

206
00:11:12,128 --> 00:11:15,536
♪Watching the brilliance of the world♪

207
00:11:15,632 --> 00:11:18,576
♪Turn into warmth in the eyes♪

208
00:11:18,864 --> 00:11:20,432
♪Holding hands tightly♪

209
00:11:20,448 --> 00:11:22,224
♪Seeing the clarity in your eyes♪

210
00:11:22,272 --> 00:11:25,792
♪It's the color of our first meeting♪

211
00:11:25,856 --> 00:11:29,232
♪Watching the twilight, vast and deep♪

212
00:11:29,296 --> 00:11:32,544
♪Turn into the desolation of the night♪

213
00:11:32,592 --> 00:11:34,249
♪Through many separations♪

214
00:11:34,250 --> 00:11:36,160
♪How can we miss it♪

215
00:11:36,190 --> 00:11:40,432
♪I am willing
to burn this life into fire♪

216
00:11:40,512 --> 00:11:42,430
♪The troubles fade away♪

217
00:11:42,430 --> 00:11:44,190
♪No more separations♪

218
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:49,392
♪Holding hands
for a lifetime is worth it♪
